    "body": "Could we add a more appropriate march when using llvm 11 on a a64fx system?  Assume change to \r\n\r\n`lib/spack/llnl/util/cpu/microarchitectures.json`\r\n\r\nAnd add under clang compiler for `a64fx`\r\n```\r\n{\r\n            \"versions\": \"11:\",\r\n            \"flags\": \"-march=a64fx\"\r\n}\r\n```\r\n",
